---
layout: default
title: Nick Piesco
excerpt: Personal website for the Wellington, New Zealand-based user experience engineer
tags:
  - home
---
<section class="home-content">
  <p class="callout">
    I’m a user experience engineer who just loves to nerd out about design, type, branding, and Oxford commas.
  </p>

  <section class="article-list">
    {% for post in collections.posts %}
      <article class="article-list-item">
        <h1 class="article-list-item-heading">
          <a href="{{ post.url }}">
            {{ post.data.title }}
          </a>
        </h1>
        <p>
          {{ post.data.excerpt | remove: '<p>' | remove: '</p>' }}
          <a href="{{ post.url }}">&#x2192;</a>
        </p>
      </article>
    {% endfor %}
  </section>
</section>
